        <updateDate>2013-11-22T20:49:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Restorative Justice in Schools Act of 2013 - Amends title II (Preparing, Training, and Recruiting High Quality Teachers and Principals) of the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 to allow local educational agencies to use title II subgrants to train school personnel in restorative justice and conflict resolution.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
